::title::
# Demo app: birthday card generator

::s1-tag::
<Tag color="gray">Parallel</Tag>

::s1-title::
Two AI tasks at once

::s1-body::
Generate an image and a message in parallel from one user prompt.

::s2-tag::
<Tag color="gray">Human Input</Tag>

::s2-title::
RSVPs as workflow events

::s2-body::
Invite friends, wait for replies, and resume the flow when real people interact.

::s3-tag::
<Tag color="gray">Scheduling</Tag>

::s3-title::
Deliver at the right moment

::s3-body::
Pause until the birthday, then send the final card and RSVP summary to the recipient.

<!--
Walk through the app shape in plain language. A user describes the kind of card they want, the app generates both an image and a message, invites friends to RSVP, waits until the birthday, and then sends the completed card to the recipient. Emphasize that this is already enough to demonstrate parallel work, human-in-the-loop behavior, and time-based scheduling in one cohesive story.
-->
---
